bookTitle: Petr Nikl: The Game of Time
bookAuthors: Petr Nikl, Jiří Přibáň, Radek Wohlmuth
Plot: This book features the painting and printmaking work of Czech artist Petr Nikl (born 1964) from the last 30 years, including a series on the subject of hatching, embryos and the mythology of origins. Writing by the artist accompanies his visual works.
